reviewText: 36 minutes long... Stereo only so there goes a star but the sound its clear.  Band members talk between the songs OMG... We're here for the music, why do I want to hear them talking about still I care less about every time I play this.  Besides it's a bad use of the technology or egotistical one of the two depending on why they did it maybe both.  So there goes another star.  If your a big fan you'll probably want to pick this up.  Fair.... nothing to get excited about.
